result:
<a-modal
    :title="title"
    :visible="visible"
    :keyboard="false"
    :maskClosable="false"
    okText="保存"
    okType="primary"
    @ok="handleOk()"
    @cancel="handleCancel()">
    <a-form
      :form="form">
      <a-form-item
        label="项目单位名称"
        v-bind="layout">
        <a-input
          type="text"
          v-decorator="[
            'name',
            {
              rules:[
                { required: true, message: '请输入项目单位名称' },
                { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
              ],
              validateTrigger: 'blur',
              initialValue: record ? record.name : null
            }
          ]">
        </a-input>
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        label="类别"
        v-bind="layout">
        <a-input
          type="text"
          v-decorator="[
            'style',
            {
              rules: [
                 { max:128,message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
              ],
              validateTrigger: 'blur',
              initialValue: record ? record.style : null
            }
          ]">
        </a-input>
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        label="项目名称"
        v-bind="layout">
        <a-input
          type="text"
          v-decorator="[
            'project_name',
            {
              rules: [
                 { max:128,message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
              ],
              validateTrigger: 'blur',
              initialValue: record ? record.project_name : null
            }
          ]">
        </a-input>
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        label="合同额"
        v-bind="layout">
        <a-input
          type="number"
          addonAfter="万元"
          v-decorator="[
            'contract_money',
            {
              rules: [
                { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
              ],
              validateTrigger: 'blur',
              initialValue: record ? record.contract_money : null
            }
          ]">
        </a-input>
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        label="结算额"
        v-bind="layout">
        <a-input
          type="number"
          addonAfter="万元"
          v-decorator="[
          'true_money',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.true_money : null
          }
        ]">
        </a-input>
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        label="本次应付"
        v-bind="layout">
        <a-input
          type="number"
          addonAfter="万元"
          v-decorator="[
          'should_money',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.should_money : null
          }
        ]">
        </a-input>
      </a-form-item>

<!--              ]"></a-date-picker>-->
<!--          </a-form-item>-->
    </a-form>
  </a-modal>
